#: budgie-welcome:452
msgid "Open the menu and search for 'Install RELEASE'"
msgstr "Ouvrez le menu et choisissez \"Installer la version\"."

#: budgie-welcome:504
msgid ""
"Seems that GNOME Software is not installed. If this problem persists even "
"after installing GNOME Software, please contact us with following error "
"message"
msgstr ""
"Il semble que GNOME Logiciels ne soit pas installé. Si le problème persiste "
"après l'avoir installé, merci de nous contacter en nous communiquant le "
"message d'erreur."

#: budgie-welcome:514
msgid ""
"Seems that App Center is not installed. If this problem persists even after "
"installing App Center, please contact us with following error message"
msgstr ""
"Il semble que le Centre d'applications ne soit pas installé. Si le problème "
"persiste après l'avoir installé, merci de nous contacter en nous "
"communiquant le message d'erreur."

#: budgie-welcome:763
msgid "Following tasks are in progress"
msgstr "Les tâches à suivre sont en cours..."

#: budgie-welcome:770 budgie-welcome:2003 budgie-welcome:2020
#: budgie-welcome:2048 budgie-welcome:2054 budgie-welcome:2568
msgid "Budgie Welcome"
msgstr "Budgie Bienvenue"

#: budgie-welcome:774
msgid "Budgie Desktop"
msgstr "Bureau Budgie"

#: budgie-welcome:902
msgid ""
"The following third-party repositories need to be added to complete the "
"installation:"
msgstr ""
"Pour terminer l'installation, il est nécessaire d'ajouter les dépôts tiers "
"suivants :"

#: budgie-welcome:955 budgie-welcome:977
msgid ""
"Third-Party repositories and their packages are not supported by Ubuntu. You"
" should only continue if you trust the maintainers of these repositories."
msgstr ""
"Les dépôts tiers et leurs paquets ne sont pas pris en charge par Ubuntu. Ne "
"continuez que si vous faites confiance aux mainteneurs de ces dépôts."

#: budgie-welcome:958 budgie-welcome:980
msgid "Continue with the installation?"
msgstr "Continuer l'installation ?"

#: budgie-welcome:964 budgie-welcome:986
msgid "Third-Party Repositories"
msgstr "Dépôts tiers"

#: budgie-welcome:975
msgid ""
"One or more packages need to be installed from a third-party repository that"
" you have previously added."
msgstr ""
"Un ou plusieurs paquets doivent être installés à partir d'un dépôt tiers que"
" vous avez préalablement ajouté."

#: budgie-welcome:1297
msgid "Welcome App"
msgstr "Application de bienvenue"

#: budgie-welcome:1671
msgid "Could not gather data."
msgstr "Impossible de récupérer les données."

#: budgie-welcome:1751
msgid "GB"
msgstr "Go"

#: budgie-welcome:1752
msgid "GiB"
msgstr "GB"

#: budgie-welcome:1753
msgid "MB"
msgstr "Mo"

#: budgie-welcome:1754
msgid "MiB"
msgstr "MB"

#: budgie-welcome:2005
msgid ""
"This snap is running on a distro that is unrecognized or on a development "
"release of Ubuntu that has not yet received its snap configuration.  Full "
"snap capabilities are unlikely to work."
msgstr ""
"Ce Snap s’exécute sur une distribution non reconnue ou sur une version de "
"développement d'Ubuntu qui n'a pas encore reçu sa configuration Snap. Il est"
" très peu probable qu'il fonctionne parfaitement. "

#: budgie-welcome:2022
msgid ""
"This snap is running on version of budgie desktop that is no longer "
"supported. Please upgrade to a supported version of the distro."
msgstr ""
"Ce Snap fonctionne sur une version de Budgie qui n'est plus supportée. "
"Faites une mise à niveau vers une version plus récente. "

#: budgie-welcome:2069
msgid "Status"
msgstr "Statut"

#: budgie-welcome:2172
msgid " is in progress. Please wait for it to complete"
msgstr " est en cours. Merci de patienter."

#: budgie-welcome:2569
msgid "Find out about your operating system"
msgstr "En savoir plus sur votre système d'exploitation"

#: budgie-welcome:2571
msgid "Budgie Makeovers & Layouts"
msgstr "Thèmes et dispositions"

#: budgie-welcome:2572
msgid "Give the desktop a makeover with new themes, icons, fonts & layouts"
msgstr ""
"Modifiez les icônes, les polices de caractères, le thème ou la disposition "
"du bureau."

#: budgie-welcome:2574
msgid "Budgie Extras"
msgstr "Applets supplémentaires"

#: budgie-welcome:2575
msgid ""
"Customize the desktop with applets and mini-applications to provide extra "
"capabilities"
msgstr ""
"Personnalisez le bureau avec des applets et de petites application pour "
"ajouter des fonctionnalités."

#: budgie-welcome:2578
msgid "Budgie Discourse"
msgstr "Budgie Discourse"

#: budgie-welcome:2579
msgid "Be part of the Ubuntu Budgie Community"
msgstr "Faites partie de la communauté Ubuntu Budgie."
